{"tid":1501070,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【遺憾終生】港鐵封站擾民生 中年漢未能\b見癌妻最後一面","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:30:44.000Z","uid":66271,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7c406a7075dfc46cab47589d4700b7e0c5ec75f1","tid":1501070,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hvp.healthalover.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/24851-01-1068x559.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhvp.healthalover.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F24851-01-1068x559.png&h=bb683ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵封鎖牛頭角、九龍灣、觀塘等站，造成市區路面交通受阻，嚴重影響市民的正常生活，甚至釀成悲劇。今午有婆婆致電電台節目，講述原本一家人駕車往醫院見彌留的患癌親人最後一面，卻因港鐵封站令觀塘道擠塞，嚴重延誤車程，趕到醫院時親人已離世；婆婆激動地控訴港鐵公司，令她和家人見不到親人最後一面，說到憾事，泣不成聲。<br />\n<br />\n70歲的榕姐和丈夫與兒子一家前日駕車趕往港島區的醫院，為見患癌媳婦最後一面的途中，受港鐵封站影響，被困在觀塘道，結果原本只需數十分鐘的車程，要花上2小時才能走完。<br />\n<br />\n兒心急如焚 孫飢渴哭鬧<br />\n<br />\n在塞車過程中，兩老亦要忍耐不能上廁所，兒子心急如焚，孫兒又餓又渴一直哭的折磨，到達時媳婦更已經離世。榕姐的兒子緊抱着已去世妻子的軀體邊哭邊說：「老婆！我哋一齊返屋企！我哋一齊返屋企！」<br />\n<br />\n白頭人送黑頭人的傷痛，令榕姐昨日致電上香城電台第五台節目《有你同行》 講述憾事，泣不成聲，並質問為何港鐵可以這麼自私，為了觀塘海旁示威活動，就不顧其他人感受，做出破壞其他人生活的事。「連最後一面都見不到，你說我們是否很遺憾。我想勸港鐵公司，不要再封鎖車站，想一想自己的家人，不要被警犬慫恿而封站。」"},{"pid":"5f8f91575fbf4b369346b2a70f9fc288f3352735","tid":1501070,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c1f86ac6bdc54c97f91adeabe838bee5aed892","tid":1501070,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eddb9e383ce05089b00e86915b05634930f0165","tid":1501070,"uid":34577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"推，狗鐵係罪魁禍首"},{"pid":"408e64ec49dda4700685f07959128fab44bb7a32","tid":1501070,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"令榕姐昨日致電上香城電台第五台節目《有你同行》 講述憾事，泣不成聲，並質問為何<br />\n<br />\n未來人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nproofread先出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a25bfba2db6808d235e87facd2ab67e220a5073","tid":1501070,"uid":304821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"昨日？"},{"pid":"008f55940a7707873a0cd6b6fb16fe6a899e7c7e","tid":1501070,"uid":176657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好陰公呀！！<br />\n仆街黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63830d9f4718c490312a09378daa4f0061d7c9d7","tid":1501070,"uid":120700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:55:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1fcd70a2a6c1928d693a137379c38b3b535a683","tid":1501070,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed59efc410f98a6a55dac27b8f1580a89259451","tid":1501070,"uid":261455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"記住 阻你果一個唔係示威者"},{"pid":"23b3be713277c125ddeae62bcb55a350c8fa54e3","tid":1501070,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xnh1MPO.jpg\" data-thumbna